SiF' Custom Upgrades List

At the time of writing this, these weapons were seen in;
• Metro - Pseudomachination (Hard Adv) -- 2024
• Scallops - Desonemebria (Easy Adv) -- 2025
• Saxford - (?) WIP
• Cyberia - 666(?) WIP
Most of these were only available in [REDACTED] servers. Reasoning not issued.

Notes:
Since they were intended to powerscale towards the intended missions, 
Most of these were designed to either provide a sidegrade of existing weapons or
provide a certain niche counterplay to existing robots in said mission.

//===============
Custom Weapon

//===============
Body Upgrade:
	 • 1.($0) Easter Egg :3c -- See Enemy HP, +75% Faster Taunts, Minigun Holster, +150% Credit Magnet Range
	 • 4.($150) +20% Melee Resistance 
	 • 3.($150) +33% Faster Holster and Deploy
	 • 4.($225) +50% Longer Melee Range
	 • 5.($300) +4 Health regenerated per sec
	 • 5.($350) +10 Max Health

	 • Scout.RESPAWN.core // ( 50% Instant Respawn | Disables reanimator )
	 	 -- 
      +50% to be instantly respawned instead of dying

      8 sec minimum respawn time
      Cannot be revived

	 • Soldier.SPLASH.core // ( +5% DMG for every enemy hit at once | -20% DMG )
	 	 -- 
      +50% damage bonus per target splashed
      +50% damage bonus per target penetrated
      Projectiles penetrate enemy players

      -20% damage vs players

	 • Pyro.REFLECT.core // ( -50% Airblast Cooldown | Airblast Cannot Push )
	 	 -- 
      -50% airblast cooldown
      Airblast gives teammates speedbost
      Reflected projectile gain +200% speed and stuns enemies

      Airblast push disabled

	 • Demoman.IMMORTALITY.core // ( Instakill Immunity | +35% Vulnerability )
	 	 -- 
      Deathblow Immune: Be put at 1 HP when about to die, unless already triggered

      -35% damage vulnerability
      -50% crit damage vulnerability

	 • Heavy.ENDURANCE.core // ( +50 HP | -20% Speed )
	 	 -- 
      +50 max health

      -20% slower move speed

	 • Engi.MORE.core // ( +50 Metal Regen, +2 Mini | -50 Max Metal )
	 	 -- 
      +2 Maximum buildable disposable Sentry 
      +50 metal regenerated per sec

      -50 less maximum metal

	 • Medic.PURE.core // ( +25% More Heal | You: -100% Overheal )
	 	 -- 
      +25% heal rate

      -100% maximum overheal

	 • Sniper.REGEN.core // ( +15% Ammo Regen | -40% Ammo )
	 	 -- 
      +15% ammo regenerated per sec

      -40% maximum ammo

	 • Spy.SPEED.core // ( +20% Speed | Self-Marked )
	 	 -- 
      +20% faster move speed

      You are Marked-For-Death 

